object.script: -- Author: Toastery -- GitHub: https://github.com/Toast732 -- Workshop: -- -- Developed & Minimized using LifeBoatAPI - Stormworks Lua plugin for VSCode -- https://code.visualstudio.com/download (search "Stormworks Lua with LifeboatAPI" extension) -- By Nameous Changey -- Minimized Size: 3073 (3387) chars bK="aggressive_road_speed" bJ="normal_offroad_speed" bI="normal_bridge_speed" bH="aggressive_offroad_speed" bG="aggressive_bridge_speed" bF="normal_road_speed" bE=57.2 bD=.1 bC=true bB=false bA=input bz=output by=math bx=by.abs bw=bz.setBool bv=by.max bu=bA.getNumber bt=bz.setNumber bs=by.random br=property.getNumber local b=0 local c=bB local d=br("random_speed_range")local e={[0]={[0]=0,[1]=0},[1]={[0]=bs(br(bF)-d,br(bF)+d),[1]=bs(br(bK)-d,br(bK)+d)},[2]={[0]=bs(br(bJ)-d,br(bJ)+d),[1]=bs(br(bH)-d,br(bH)+d)},[3]={[0]=bs(br(bI)-d,br(bI)+d),[1]=bs(br(bG)-d,br(bG)+d)}}function f(g,h)return bs()*(h-g)+g end function i(j,k,l,m)return by.deg(by.atan(l-j,m-k))end function n(l,m,j,k)return by.sqrt((j-l)^2+(k-m)^2)end function o(p,q)if p>q then return bC else return bB end end function r(s,t,u,v)if not t then bt(1,s)else local w=br("aggressive_behaviour")local x=1 if w==0 then x=bu(13)elseif w==1 then x=0 end local y=1 if v<100 and x==0 then y=v/100 elseif v<50 then y=v/50 end local z=bu(14)if s>0 then local A=br("minimum_speed_random_range")local B=br("minimum_speed")+f(-A,-A)if x==1 then B=B*1.5 end bt(1,bv(e[z][x]/bv(u/90,1)*(y),B))else bt(1,0)end end end local C=br("turning_rate_random_range")local D=br("turning_rate")+f(-C,-C)function E(s,F)if not F then bt(2,s)else local G=b-bv(by.min(b-s,D),-D)bt(2,G)b=G end end function onTick()local H=br("steering_type")local I=br("front_dist_tolerance")local J=br("front_down_dist_tolerance")local K=br("rear_dist_tolerance")local L=br("rear_down_dist_tolerance")local M=br("wall_safe_dist")local N=br("ground_safe_dist")local O=br("tank_turn_speed")local P=bA.getBool(1)local Q=bu(1)local R=bu(2)local S=bu(3)local T=bu(4)local U=bu(15)local V=bu(16)local W=bu(5)*-360 local X=i(Q,R,S,T)local Y=bu(6)local Z=bu(7)local bb=bu(8)local bc=bu(9)local bd=bu(10)local be=bu(11)local bf=Y-I local bg=Z-J local bh=bb-J local bi=bc-K local bj=bd-L local bk=be-L if S~=0 or T~=0 then v=n(Q,R,S,T)bt(5,v)if v>2 and P then bw(1,bC)bt(3,W)local bl=X-W bt(5,X)bt(6,bl)if H==0 then local bm=br("steering_max_angle")local bn=bu(12)local bo=n(Q,R,U,V)if bl>91 or bl<-91 then if not c then bw(2,bC)r(0)E(0,bC)bw(3,bC)if bn<bD then c=bC bw(3,bB)end else bw(3,bB)E(-(bl/90*bm/bE),bC)r(1,bC,bl,bo)bw(2,bC)c=bC end bt(7,1)elseif o(bf,M)then if c then bw(2,bB)r(0,bC,bl,bo)E(0,bC)bw(3,bC)if bn<bD then c=bB bw(3,bB)end else bw(3,bB)E((bl/90*bm/bE),bC)r(1,bC,bl,bo)bw(2,bB)c=bB end bt(7,2)elseif o(bi,M)then if not c then bw(2,bC)r(0)E(0,bC)bw(3,bC)if bn<bD then c=bC bw(3,bB)end else bw(3,bB)E(-(bl/90*bm/bE),bC)r(1,bC,bl,bo)bw(2,bC)c=bC end bt(7,3)else bw(2,bB)bw(1,bB)r(0)E(0,bC)bt(7,4)end elseif H==1 then local bp=1 if v<50 then bp=v/25 end local bq=1 if bx(bl)<50 then bq=bx(bl)/25 end bt(4,bq)if bl<2 and bl>-2 then if o(bf,M)then r(1*bp)E(0)end elseif bl<182 and bl>178 then if o(bf,M)then r(-1*bp)E(0)end elseif bl>0 and 180>bl then if o(N,bg)and o(N,bk)then E(-O*bq)if bq==1 then r(0)else r((.08/bq))end end else if o(N,bh)and o(N,bj)then E(O*bq)if bq==1 then r(0)else r((.08/bq))end end end end else bt(7,5)bw(1,bB)end end end
